    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "oq3_text",
      "x": 113.86954115226814,
      "y": 895.2981741737306,
      "width": 401.953125,
      "height": 175,
      "text": "Q3: If customers buy standalone burst\nupgrade, do we also increase their\nmonthly quota? They would of course want/need\nincreased monthly quota, but omitting it from the\nstand-alone burst upgrade package would provide\nmore incentive toward tier upgrade instead.\n\nE.g. A Pro Tier customer buys 2x burst multiplier\nfor all their endpoints [Option 2]\n— should their monthly quota also grow 2x?",
      "originalText": "Q3: If customers buy standalone burst\nupgrade, do we also increase their\nmonthly quota? They would of course want/need\nincreased monthly quota, but omitting it from the\nstand-alone burst upgrade package would provide\nmore incentive toward tier upgrade instead.\n\nE.g. A Pro Tier customer buys 2x burst multiplier\nfor all their endpoints [Option 2]\n— should their monthly quota also grow 2x?",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
