      "y": 903.1442778259986,
      "width": 410,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Q4: Do we want to make the tier upgrade\nmore favorable/attractive than\nstandalone burst limit purchases? Why?\n\nGoal: Pro → Enterprise upgrade should be more\ncost-effective than buying standalone burst add-ons",
